div1.p: United States of America, Western DISTRICT OF Washington} ss:

I hereby certify and return that I served the annexed Writ of Habeas Corpus on the therein- named Henry M. White US Imm Commissioner by serving John H. Sargent his asst
by handing to and leaving a true and correct copy thereof with John H. Sargent asst
